WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: the operator side — bootstrap a tailnet from nothing.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: a fresh host runs octravpn-node init for the control plane.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: the headscale-rs config is templated from the demo defaults.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: bring the control plane up under systemd.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: a DERP sidecar boots beside it for NAT-traversal fallback.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: mint the first preauth key — the seed for the operator host.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: the operator host itself joins, becoming peer-zero.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:15.000
narrator: from here on, new users are one preauth key each.
